data.description: CONVENTIONAL FINANCING OR CASH ONLY. Home is sold “as is” and priced accordingly.  One of a kind custom-built, center-hall farm-house with almost 4,000 square feet of living space on two-levels.  Home needs love and some work but is in good shape.  Upper level has two large master bedrooms (30x12) with private baths and two additional large bedrooms (15x15 and 15x12) sharing a full hallway bath. Extra-large kitchen (30x12) with walk-in pantry, and breakfast room. Separate dining and living rooms, large family room with brick wood-burning fireplace and a huge (24x24) recreation room off of the family room. Beautiful hardwood floors on main level. 2 sets of shutter doors leading out to the front porch. Very nice one-acre lot.  Check home prices next door up to $700K.  Home is currently on well but seller will pay for public water hook-up. Seller will backfill pool.
